description: Jakob was infatuated by Brysen’s good looks and endearing charm, “He’s so cute…look at this piece of man meat!” Brysen touched his ass, “Nice piece of man meat down here…” They have met before in Puerto Rico, but didn’t really get a chance to film together as much as they wanted to…that is, until now, and it was just what they wanted!
title: Jakob & Brysen: Bareback
